### Reproduction link
[https://stackblitz.com/edit/ng-zorro-antd-ivy-yvnj3s?file=package.json,src%2Fapp%2Fapp.component.ts](https://stackblitz.com/edit/ng-zorro-antd-ivy-yvnj3s?file=package.json,src%2Fapp%2Fapp.component.ts)

### Steps to reproduce
#### 在我的项目中有这种需求，点击DatePicker的clear清除图标，需要弹窗提示用户
#### 但是弹出Modal或drawer弹窗，弹窗不正常显示
#####我觉得和ChangeDetectionStrategy.OnPush有关， 我拉下源码查看了一下
```
updateInputValue(): void {
    const newValue = this.datePickerService.value;
    if (this.isRange) {
      this.inputValue = newValue ? (newValue as CandyDate[]).map((v) => this.formatValue(v)) : ['', ''];
    } else {
      this.inputValue = this.formatValue(newValue as CandyDate);
    }
    // this.cdr.markForCheck();
    this.cdr.detectChanges()
 }
```
将变更检测方式markForCheck改成detectChanges,Modal或drawer正常显示
请问还要更好的方式去实现吗？
##### 目前在我的项目中我是通过这样方式解决的，它同样对我有效
```
constructor(
    private _service: NzModalService,
    private zone: NgZone,
  ) {}
this.zone.run(() => {
   const _modal = this._service.create({
      nzTitle: '123',
   });
});
```
tips: 我在13.0.0版本中发现是正常的

### What is expected?
Modal 或 drawer正常打开

### What is actually happening?
click datePicker clear button, the Modal Abnormal open

| Environment | Info |
|---|---|
| ng-zorro-antd | 13.4.0 |
| Browser | chrome |

